value.subject: CSC Discussion

body.content:
Israel,

 

Talked with the team today and Rick has bandwidth to run point on CSC.  I realize you’re up in Redmond this week – do you have availability for a quick touch point?  Wanting to bring him further up to speed and get him introduced to Ivan and Ajit.

 

Could potentially do later today if that gets it in before you start tomorrow.

 

Thanks,

Steven

value.subject: OMS Tech Fridays - Fall Season

body.content:
Sending New Invite as previous was corrupted

 

Hello,

 

Please join us every other Friday for an hour focused on technical information regarding Microsoft’s business continuity and disaster recovery solutions including:

Azure Site Recovery (ASR), Azure Backup (AB), Operational Insights (OI), Azure Automation (AA), and related technologies. 

 

Our goal in this series will be to deliver deep technical content on a specific component or aspect of a component each time. 

 

Every call will follow this basic outline:

 

-          OMS Overview (10-15 minutes)

-          Technical Deep Dive/Partner Focus of the Week (30 minutes)

-          Q&A (10-15 minutes)

 

We will post the specific topic being covered a few days prior as well as recordings and other materials from past discussions here:

http://aka.ms/OMSFridays.

 

Note that this discussion is open to anyone and everyone interested in learning technical details about OMS.  Please feel free to share this series with whomever may be interested.
